Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:10.17,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}出會いは　shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:43.04,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:15.26,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}まだ知らない世界へ歩き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:43.04,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.80,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}無謀な挑戦者さ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:43.04,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:23.14,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}手にした刃で明日を切り開けばいいんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:43.04,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:25.23,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}誰かのもんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:43.04,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:29.02,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}自分だけのストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:37.72,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}比心中描繪的意象更遙遠的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:44.14,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}在一筆筆敘寫  那真實還在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.02,0:22:48.02,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}如無盡的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:53.07,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}來將各自的自尊心研磨透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:58.07,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}敞開任何言語之類的裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:07.50,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相互碰撞 相互摩擦 rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:10.17,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相遇是 shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:15.26,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}向未知的世界邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.80,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}無謀的挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:23.14,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}只要用手中的刀劈開明天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:25.23,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}這並不是別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:29.02,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}是只屬於自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:34.98,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}因為我們都是未經琢磨的鑽石！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:43.04,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:34.98,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}cause we are still rough diamonds on the road!
